  <brief_title>Impact of General Anaesthetics on Excitability of the Peripheral Sensory Nerve</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Zurich</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Zurich</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the effect of general anaesthetics on nerve
      excitability. We use the method of threshold tracking to measure selected parameters of nerve
      excitability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
